	<section anchor="Security" title="Security Considerations">
     <t>
      At the time of writing of this document there are no known weak keys
      for Camellia and no security problems have been found with Camellia 
      (see <xref target ="NESSIE"/>, <xref target="CRYPTREC"/>, and <xref target="Research"/>).
     </t>
      <t>
      	The security considerations in RFC 5289 <xref target="RFC5289" /> apply to this document as well. 
      </t>
